<p>[3] Berg, Janine, Marianne Furrer, Ellie Harmon, Uma Rani, and M. Six Silberman. Digital labour platforms and the future of work: Towards decent work in the online world. Geneva: International Labour Office, 2018. </p>
<p>[4] Gray, Mary L., and Siddharth Suri. "The humans working behind the AI curtain." Harvard Business Review 9 (2017): 2-5. </p>
